                "id": "s1",
                "text_en": "Take a small element of the string. Its mass is zero."
              },
              {
                "id": "s2",
                "text_en": "Apply Newton's second law. Net force equals mass times acceleration. Mass is zero, so net force must be zero."
              },
              {
                "id": "s3",
                "text_en": "That forces T one and T two to be equal — the tensions on either side of the element must match."
              },
              {
                "id": "s4",
